{"tid":1041343,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"過左半年，終於知道係邊個令你離開我","createTime":"2019-02-28T18:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T21:04:05.000Z","uid":30094,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"beed35c55e906cb902599ec328c4fac5f9bddd07","tid":1041343,"uid":30094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:06:14.000Z","msg":"分左手半年，到今日終於比我見到半年前令你開始嫌我煩，嫌我無用嘅人係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢，我嘅關心變左做管得好嚴<br />\n因為佢，我揾你你開始覺得好厭<br />\n一次又一次嘅隱瞞，我一次又一次咁發現，然後一次又一次嘅原諒，到最後你都係跟佢走左<br />\n你可以開開心心咁離開，繼續同新男友一齊，同朋友一齊嘻嘻哈哈咁過<br />\n我為左你幾乎眾叛親離，身邊冇剩底幾多個人<br />\n過左半年，我以為我自己已經平伏左好多<br />\n到今日又跌返落谷底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人生幾時先完"},{"pid":"49ed138926befff4b59099fcd002dea3e76583d0","tid":1041343,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人叫你 all in"},{"pid":"142f40bbcee821ae305ba32fba5e672580b21584","tid":1041343,"uid":182676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:09:20.000Z","msg":"大世界裡會找到別個"},{"pid":"ac34ca997a063e7333b35bc7123036127b7a2bf5","tid":1041343,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:12:54.000Z","msg":"點解條女出軌, 眾叛親離果個反而係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb5dd3ec6da3a876ac4f2b1769fcbb4c1330259","tid":1041343,"uid":30094,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49ed138926befff4b59099fcd002dea3e76583d0","tid":1041343,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇人叫你 all in"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:14:35.000Z","msg":"你啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我當初都以為自己年紀都應該要諗得長遠D<br />\n所以all in左係佢身上<br />\n結果就係輸到仆街"},{"pid":"709929351e5241e37f62a81547322864fee34b28","tid":1041343,"uid":236401,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c99aa81cd5443c59fd1b8a89ae01d12e0c6df836","tid":1041343,"uid":30094,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"ac34ca997a063e7333b35bc7123036127b7a2bf5","tid":1041343,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:12:54.000Z","msg":"點解條女出軌, 眾叛親離果個反而係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"我本身同屋企人關係就好一般，<br />\n有一段時間佢去過我到住，我家人同佢唔太夾，而當時嘅我決定避免呢個問題，所以同佢搬左出去，我自己唔係揾得好多，所以我家人好反對，果陣時嘈得好勁，但我都係做左<br />\n之後開始好多親戚都有打電話黎話我點解要為左個女仔同自己父母撐得咁行，不如勸下我ex大家互相遷就下就算啦<br />\n但個結果就係我依然好強硬，佢地都覺得我好不孝，之後開始慢慢咁冇人再理過我<br />\n而家分手後，我返左阿媽到住返，佢地都同意，但個關係已經變到好差，當我係透明冇咩分別"},{"pid":"ee4adde8bc16764702c48c28dad6b86fe0095426","tid":1041343,"uid":30094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"709929351e5241e37f62a81547322864fee34b28","tid":1041343,"uid":236401,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:19:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:30:02.000Z","msg":"邊到得罪左你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1101510360c3dc828fb420351007d7e00d2a6e12","tid":1041343,"uid":57255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c99aa81cd5443c59fd1b8a89ae01d12e0c6df836","tid":1041343,"uid":30094,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"ac34ca997a063e7333b35bc7123036127b7a2bf5","tid":1041343,"uid":57255,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:12:54.000Z","msg":"點解條女出軌, 眾叛親離果個反而係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"我本身同屋企人關係就好一般，<br />\n有一段時間佢去過我到住，我家人同佢唔太夾，而當時嘅我決定避免呢個問題，所以同佢搬左出去，我自己唔係揾得好多，所以我家人好反對，果陣時嘈得好勁